- Act as a brand ambassador, representing grape at industry events.

- 5+ years of experience as a TA Business Partner/Recruiter in-house with experience in recruiting and hiring internationally. Ideally within a fast-scaling start-up, SAAS, or tech-driven environment;
- A driven professional with a passion for talent sourcing. Finding and hiring great talent is what drives you;
- A solid understanding of data-driven hiring: you use data to optimize recruitment efforts in areas such as: time to hire, hiring forecast, cost per hire;
- Proven experience in IT/Tech recruitment - comfortable speaking with engineers, product managers, and technical leads;
- Ability to build strong relationships with all levels of stakeholders;
- Experience in recruitment within the insurance industry is a nice to have;
- Highly service-oriented, a high level of professionalism, integrity, and confidentiality;
- Excellent communication skills with fluency in English and German (verbal and written).

